---
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />

    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    />

    <meta
      name="description"
      content="GO・KI・GEN TIME — フラヴィア・ニシムラの料理、庭、暮らしの物語。"
    />

    <title>GO・KI・GEN TIME | フラヴィア・ニシムラ</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />

    <link
      rel="preconnect"
      href="https://fonts.gstatic.com"
      crossorigin
    />

    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style>
      :root {
        --cream: #faf7f1;
        --paper: #fffdf8;
        --ink: #4a332c;
        --muted: #806f68;
        --line: #ddd0c6;
        --accent: #a56a4d;
        --accent-soft: #efe2d8;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--cream);
        color: var(--ink);
        font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      img {
        display: block;
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .site-header {
        position: fixed;
        z-index: 100;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        left: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 22px 48px;
        background: rgba(250, 247, 241, 0.93);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(221, 208, 198, 0.8);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      }

      .logo {
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .menu {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        gap: 30px;
      }

      .menu a {
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
      }

      .menu a:hover {
        opacity: 0.55;
      }

      .hero {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 100vh;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 150px 30px 90px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-inner {
        width: min(100%, 1000px);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 22px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.3em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .brand {
        display: block;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(58px, 10vw, 138px);
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        line-height: 0.82;
      }

      .brand-time {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 34px;
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 54px);
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.55em;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .hero-description {
        width: min(100%, 620px);
        margin: 52px auto 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 2.15;
      }

      .hero-signature {
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: 20px;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 42px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        min-width: 180px;
        min-height: 50px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 14px 24px;
        border: 1px solid var(--ink);
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition:
          background 0.25s ease,
          color 0.25s ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--paper);
      }

      .button-soft {
        border-color: var(--line);
        background: var(--paper);
      }

      .section {
        padding: 120px 30px;
      }

      .section-inner {
        width: min(100%, 1100px);
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .section-heading {
        margin-bottom: 64px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .section-number {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      }

      .section-heading h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 72px);
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .section-heading p {
        width: min(100%, 600px);
        margin: 24px auto 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 2;
      }

      .story {
        background: var(--paper);
      }

      .story-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 90px;
      }

      .story-visual {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 520px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 55px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(
            145deg,
            rgba(165, 106, 77, 0.18),
            rgba(239, 226, 216, 0.4)
          );
      }

      .story-mark {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(72px, 10vw, 130px);
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        line-height: 0.85;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .story-text .eyebrow {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .story-text h2 {
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 68px);
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.05;
      }

      .story-text p {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 2.15;
      }

      .library {
        background: var(--cream);
      }

      .book-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 0.85fr) minmax(300px, 1.15fr);
        overflow: hidden;
        background: var(--paper);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .book-cover {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 620px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 52px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(
            circle at top left,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8),
            transparent 45%
          ),
          linear-gradient(145deg, #ead8c9, #c99676);
      }

      .cover-inner {
        display: flex;
        width: min(100%, 330px);
        aspect-ratio: 0.72;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 44px 34px;
        background: #f9f1e8;
        border: 1px solid rgba(74, 51, 44, 0.22);
        box-shadow: 0 28px 60px rgba(74, 51, 44, 0.18);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .cover-small {
        font-size: 9px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.23em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .cover-title {
        margin: auto 0;
        font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(25px, 3vw, 38px);
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .cover-author {
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: 15px;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      }

      .book-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 70px;
      }

      .book-label {
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 10px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .book-content h3 {
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        font-size: clamp(27px, 4vw, 44px);
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .book-content p {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 2.15;
      }

      .book-details {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
        margin: 32px 0 38px;
        padding: 26px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .book-detail span {
        display: block;
      }

      .detail-label {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 9px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .detail-value {
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .book-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .philosophy {
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .quote {
        width: min(100%, 850px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 74px);
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.15;
      }

      .quote-japanese {
        width: min(100%, 600px);
        margin: 36px auto 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        line-height: 2.2;
      }

      .about-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 90px;
      }

      .about-name {
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 86px);
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 0.95;
      }

      .about-text p {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 2.15;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 70px 30px 40px;
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--paper);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer-logo {
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: clamp(35px, 5vw, 56px);
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      }

      .footer-text {
        margin: 22px auto 0;
        color: rgba(255, 253, 248, 0.7);
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      }

      .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 28px;
        margin-top: 32px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .footer-links a {
        font-size: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .copyright {
        margin-top: 55px;
        color: rgba(255, 253, 248, 0.45);
        font-size: 9px;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      }

      @media (max-width: 850px) {
        .site-header {
          padding: 19px 22px;
        }

        .logo {
          font-size: 17px;
        }

        .menu {
          gap: 15px;
        }

        .menu a {
          font-size: 9px;
        }

        .menu a:nth-child(2) {
          display: none;
        }

        .hero {
          padding-top: 135px;
        }

        .story-grid,
        .about-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 50px;
        }

        .story-visual {
          min-height: 390px;
        }

        .book-card {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .book-cover {
          min-height: auto;
          padding: 48px 26px;
        }

        .cover-inner {
          width: min(100%, 280px);
        }

        .book-content {
          padding: 48px 30px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 520px) {
        .site-header {
          align-items: center;
        }

        .menu {
          gap: 12px;
        }

        .menu a {
          font-size: 8px;
          letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        .brand {
          font-size: 56px;
        }

        .brand-time {
          margin-top: 25px;
          font-size: 25px;
          letter-spacing: 0.35em;
        }

        .hero-description {
          font-size: 13px;
        }

        .section {
          padding: 90px 20px;
        }

        .book-details {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 18px;
        }

        .button {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="logo" href="/ja">GO・KI・GEN TIME</a>

      <nav class="menu" aria-label="メインメニュー">
        <a href="#story">物語</a>
        <a href="#library">ライブラリー</a>
        <a href="#about">プロフィール</a>
        <a href="/">PT</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-inner">
          <p class="eyebrow">Born in Tainai, Niigata</p>

          <h1>
            <span class="brand">GO・KI・GEN</span>
            <span class="brand-time">TIME</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-description">
            育てること、焼くこと、つくること。<br />
            日々の小さな時間を大切にしながら、料理と庭、
            そして暮らしの物語を綴っています。
          </p>

          <p class="hero-signature">Flavia Nishimura</p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button" href="#library">本を見る</a>
            <a class="button button-soft" href="/library">Library</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section story" id="story">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <div class="story-grid">
            <div class="story-visual">
              <div class="story-mark">
                A new<br />
                memory<br />
                unfolding
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="story-text">
              <p class="eyebrow">Growing, baking, creating</p>

              <h2>特別な日を待たない暮らし。</h2>

              <p>
                誰かが来る日だけではなく、
                自分ひとりのためにも丁寧に料理をつくる。
                花を飾り、好きな器を選び、
                その日の時間を静かに味わう。
              </p>

              <p>
                GO・KI・GEN TIMEは、
                そんな小さな喜びを集める場所です。
                新潟県胎内市の古民家カフェと庭から、
                レシピや物語をお届けします。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section library" id="library">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="section-number">01</span>
            <h2>Library</h2>

            <p>
              料理を通して、自分のための時間を育てるための一冊。
            </p>
          </div>

          <article class="book-card">
            <div class="book-cover">
              <div class="cover-inner">
                <span class="cover-small">GO・KI・GEN TIME</span>

                <div class="cover-title">
                  一人のための<br />
                  小さなお菓子
                </div>

                <span class="cover-author">Flavia Nishimura</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="book-content">
              <div class="book-label">The first book</div>

              <h3>一人のための小さなお菓子</h3>

              <p>
                一人で過ごす時間にも、
                きちんとお菓子をつくって楽しみたい。
                そんな思いから生まれた、
                小さな分量のデザートレシピ集です。
              </p>

              <p>
                食べきれる量で、無駄を少なく。
                特別な道具を増やさず、
                日常の中で気軽につくれる10のレシピを収録しています。
              </p>

              <div class="book-details">
                <div class="book-detail">
                  <span class="detail-label">Recipes</span>
                  <span class="detail-value">10 recipes</span>
                </div>

                <div class="book-detail">
                  <span class="detail-label">Language</span>
                  <span class="detail-value">日本語</span>
                </div>

                <div class="book-detail">
                  <span class="detail-label">Theme</span>
                  <span class="detail-value">一人分のお菓子</span>
                </div>

                <div class="book-detail">
                  <span class="detail-label">Author</span>
                  <span class="detail-value">Flavia Nishimura</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="book-actions">
                <a class="button" href="/library">本のページへ</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section philosophy">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <div class="quote">
            The present<br />
            needs no occasion.
          </div>

          <p class="quote-japanese">
            今日という時間に、特別な理由はいりません。<br />
            自分のために整え、つくり、味わうこと。<br />
            それだけで、日常は少し豊かになります。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-name">
              Flavia<br />
              Nishimura
            </div>

            <div class="about-text">
              <p>
                ブラジル生まれ、日本在住。
                料理人、パン職人、レシピクリエイター、
                そして新潟県胎内市にある古民家カフェ
                「Kuma Café」のオーナーです。
              </p>

              <p>
                料理、庭、古い家、季節の移ろい。
                手を動かしながら生まれる日々の物語を、
                本と写真と言葉で記録しています。
              </p>

              <p>
                GO・KI・GEN TIMEは、
                誰かを待たずに自分のための時間を楽しむ、
                小さなきっかけを届けるための場所です。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">GO・KI・GEN TIME</div>

      <p class="footer-text">
        Growing, baking, creating — from Tainai, Niigata.
      </p>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/ja">日本語</a>
        <a href="/">Português</a>
        <a href="/library">Library</a>
      </div>

      <div class="copyright">
        © 2026 FLAVIA NISHIMURA. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>